  %h2{:class=>"signup_header"} Instructions
  %p
    %div{:style=>"font-weight:bold;"}How can I subscribe to the Sizzix.com Scoop email newsletter?
    Subscribing to the Sizzix.com Scoop is easy! Simply sign up now at Sizzix.com or just enter your email address in the bottom right corner of any page.
    %br
    %br
    %div{:style=>"font-weight:bold;"}How do I unsubscribe to the Sizzix.com Scoop email newsletter?
    To remove your subscription to the Sizzix.com Scoop, please follow the unsubscribe link in your Scoop email. Or, please log in at Sizzix.com and go to My Account page and uncheck the Subscription box.
    %br
    %br
    %div{:style=>"font-weight:bold;"}After subscribing, how can I ensure that I will continue to receive my Sizzix.com Scoop newsletter?
    To ensure that your Sizzix.com Scoop newsletter is delivered to your inbox, not as spam, please add sizzixscoop@lyris.sizzix.com to your email address book as soon as possible.My Scoop was delivered to my Bulk or Junk mail folder.
