    %br
    %div{:style=>"font-weight:bold;"}How can I prevent this from happening?
    Some email providers deliver Sizzix.com Scoop emails to your Bulk or Junk mail folders. Please flag these emails appropriately so that these emails are delivered to your inbox on time.
 
